{"tid":1717537,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"到底點樣先可以有效開花？！","createTime":"2019-11-13T15:36:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T15:43:44.000Z","uid":36563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b54784ea1a8211621ddc03f526a72c73980ddd73","tid":1717537,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:36:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">前言</span></ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢幾個月大家都開花開到識結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過似乎大家已經習慣咗開花既地點  冇乜轉陣<br />\n甚至開始有中意打陣地既傾向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n與此同時，狗隻都開始以逸待勞，去哂各區開花熱點set陣大圍捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以，我地都應該要思考下<br />\n點樣有效開花之餘又要減低手足被咬既風險<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>重點</ins></span></span></strong><br />\n就住以上既形勢，我有3個建議:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 攻其不備  放棄慣常地點</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n集合地點需要定期更改，以防狗隻已熟悉地形，甚至未齊人已經佈好陣守株待兔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n開花期間亦應該不時轉陣，<span style=\"color: red;\">盡量嘗試去一啲從來冇去過既地方，屋邨，馬路 (令到狗隻出奇不意)  </span><br />\n<br />\n參考出面巴打既Post，區議會選區係一個幾好指南<br />\n<br />\n<em><ins>參考資料: 區議會一般選舉選區分界圖</ins></em><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eac.hk/ch/distco/2019dc_elect_map.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eac.hk%2Fch%2Fdistco%2F2019dc_elect_map.htm&d=jGmFyvXa%2BxCeqK61Wy4ey8%2BSO5qySt9BI5W58Aqq%2Fug%3D&h=d478746f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eac.hk/ch/distco/2019dc_elect_map.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>2. Hit and Run</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個講到口臭，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大家無非必要唔好迷戀陣地</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n的確有啲地方我認同係有守既價值 (例如暴大二橋)<br />\n但好多時既陣地係冇太大既戰略意義<br />\n結果好易比時間狗隻set陣包圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍狗屋就更加冇意思，狗不痛不癢，佢地仲有無限補給<br />\n除非大家已有攻城決心，否則避免圍狗屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要記住，我地出嚟並唔係搏比狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>3. 建設可持續RB</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n係呢幾個月既抗爭之後<br />\n相信大家都會發現，RB既材料係一啲熱門地方已經買少見少，<br />\n就算而家只係普通行個街都未必再有垃圾桶比你掉垃圾<br />\n<br />\n加上最近既港豬藍絲都開始會落手清RB<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而我地亦預見到呢一場會係一場持久戰，暫時都未見到會完既一日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以，開花時起既RB，必須要由一啲就地取材既簡陋RB，進化成一啲<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>難以即時清理 (至少唔係徒手或者一腳就可以踢走推開)，甚至係半永久/永久既RB</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算真係用雜物set，記得<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">圍城必闕</span></strong></span>，留返條生口等自私既港豬藍絲懶得落去清<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例子就有:<br />\n<br />\n現代鐵蒺藜<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M7Jcz1r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM7Jcz1r.png&h=815c289e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n石屎躉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GeX5awJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGeX5awJ.jpg&h=13e6547f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kr9fxK4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkr9fxK4.jpg&h=c5cc9c0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鑽地師，令路面變月球表面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LZigheU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLZigheU.jpg&h=08312bbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有其他等大家去發揮<br />\n<br />\n<em>同時可以參考下二戰時啲軍隊點樣set RB </em><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/British_anti-invasion_preparations_of_the_Second_World_War\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FBritish_anti-invasion_preparations_of_the_Second_World_War&d=jGmFyvXa%2BxCeqK61Wy4ey8%2BSO5qySt9BI5W58Aqq%2Fug%3D&h=f5b3cb21\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/British_anti-invasion_preparations_of_the_Second_World_War</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家開花可以有進化做法，達至開花2.0！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港  時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"824875c73cb03f0d0b216b8b3b43ef9d503baa85","tid":1717537,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:38:20.000Z","msg":"仲有一樣想講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係盡量避免深夜繼續開花，因為冇哂街坊和理非掩護，就好易比狗無差別咁咬，避免正面交鋒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c365b60724ecbfd2f54631ccdc469b9726f36188","tid":1717537,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:38:34.000Z","msg":"自推10連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3053dc53def9c0a4d8e5e5fd33afb936b62ab0b","tid":1717537,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:38:44.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca9379a8ca849818bd91b906e9c694ce776b30b","tid":1717537,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:38:54.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed074322bb980575441e141ba288953d716e317","tid":1717537,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:39:50.000Z","msg":"本人絕不鼓勵大家做犯法嘢，以上只供天馬行空紙上談兵用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e1dd88c264f0a0f7c58a1523e91a3c581e201e","tid":1717537,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:40:01.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"589552d801206080e8075ec62ee5c3269680b395","tid":1717537,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:40:12.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f238cc78783634c4cac1480023a1340c8f95c83f","tid":1717537,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:40:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf9b44b56504712396a9e8cf8b67389f495de20","tid":1717537,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:41:37.000Z","msg":"完全推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a856ab486c0bfc0fc415ca9cd672701cbc136677","tid":1717537,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:42:03.000Z","msg":"有冇人幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0857d45be2b4bdc6d39a75b7b5e4bb7da83474fc","tid":1717537,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:42:19.000Z","msg":"好似10連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd94c62d00c036a9398866e7da18d4efd3242586","tid":1717537,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:42:39.000Z","msg":"ok 10連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d4875c2220a4967a000a1d052e1fc8c5dbde7f9","tid":1717537,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:43:03.000Z","msg":"都係推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb3f2234f362b97a851b4d4923bdf7845579efc"